            "stanza_text": "Voyez, amis, cette barque légère\nQui de la vie essaie encor les flots :\nElle contient gentille passagère ;\nAh ! Soyons-en les premiers matelots.\nDéja les eaux l'enlèvent au rivage\nQue doucement elle fuit pour toujours.\nNous qui voyons commencer le voyage,\nPar nos chansons égayons-en le cours."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Déja le sort a soufflé dans les voiles ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Déja l'espoir prépare les agrès,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Et nous promet, à l'éclat des étoiles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Une mer calme et des vents doux et frais.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Fuyez, fuyez, oiseaux d'un noir présage :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Cette nacelle appartient aux amours.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Nous qui voyons commencer le voyage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Par nos chansons égayons-en le cours.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Déja le sort a soufflé dans les voiles ;\nDéja l'espoir prépare les agrès,\nEt nous promet, à l'éclat des étoiles,\nUne mer calme et des vents doux et frais.\nFuyez, fuyez, oiseaux d'un noir présage :\nCette nacelle appartient aux amours.\nNous qui voyons commencer le voyage,\nPar nos chansons égayons-en le cours."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Au mât propice attachant leurs guirlandes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Oui, les amours prennent part au travail.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Aux chastes sœurs on a fait des offrandes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Et l'amitié se place au gouvernail.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
