                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Nous qui voyons commencer le voyage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Par nos chansons égayons-en le cours.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Au mât propice attachant leurs guirlandes,\nOui, les amours prennent part au travail.\nAux chastes sœurs on a fait des offrandes,\nEt l'amitié se place au gouvernail.\nBacchus lui-même anime l'équipage,\nQui des plaisirs invoque le secours.\nNous qui voyons commencer le voyage,\nPar nos chansons égayons-en le cours."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Qui vient encor saluer la nacelle ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "C'est le malheur bénissant la vertu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Et demandant que du bien fait par elle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Sur cet enfant le prix soit répandu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
